{"id": 2850, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今为了防止“数字失联”，你都用了哪些招？", "description": "如何确保“彼此在线上始终能找到对方”，还真是个问题。（题图来自：iStock ️©️ Creative-Touch）", "record_count": 6554, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190317204548CndbptQIxs2jR4vh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-20T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5535, "title": "现如今为了防止“数字失联”，你都用了哪些招？", "content": "现如今为了防止“数字失联”，你都用了哪些招？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 333607, "content": "很久没刷到某个人的更新，会点进 ta 主页看下是否安好", "image": "img/option/option/201903181033004OrGeW35ZYtJMRwF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333605, "content": "看到喜欢的博主，会把 ta 的小号也一并关注了", "image": "img/option/option/201903181035099EeTfcyDj2uYiVhU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333606, "content": "除了关注博主本人，还会顺带关注几个 ta 的朋友", "image": "img/option/option/201903181033491R50eXmsnEwBzNW4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333600, "content": "跟谈得来的朋友，交换微信之外的社交媒体帐号", "image": "img/option/option/201903181044449jLcWomG4hxCABy2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333601, "content": "不定期在好友群里说几句话，稍微刷刷存在感", "image": "img/option/option/201903181038181z3ydnEx547KShuf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333602, "content": "偶尔给不太联系的熟人点赞，表达“我并没有屏蔽你”", "image": "img/option/option/20190318103633jtWPRs6nZfQGgm8b.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333603, "content": "弃用 QQ 之后，会在签名里写上“有事微信找我”", "image": "img/option/option/20190318103623panqCbtfSNj7FUxQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333604, "content": "把微信昵称改成“二狗-休假中”，表示“度假中欢迎留言”", "image": "img/option/option/20190318103608HfXdzNWVlDOu7xer.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 333608, "content": "都不会，我还是喜欢顺其自然", "image": "img/option/option/20190318103238Yx2EH1z94BDNQrMO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}